column2: bytesAllowed        Number of total bytes allowed in this region.
column3: byteCount        Number of bytes in region.
column4: lruEvictions        Number of total entry evictions triggered by LRU.
column5: lruDestroys        Number of entries destroyed in the region through both destroy cache operations and eviction. Reset to zero each time it exceeds lruDestroysLimit.
column6: lruDestroysLimit        Maximum number of entry destroys triggered by LRU before scan occurs.
column7: lruEvaluations        Number of entries evaluated during LRU operations.
column8: lruGreedyReturns        Number of non-LRU entries evicted during LRU operations
